<p>We have as many roads in the United States as we have streams and rivers.</p>

<p>Produced by Caroline Kanner and Jackson Roach, with original music by Jackson Roach. Edited by Liza Yeager and Mitchell Johnson, with editorial oversight from Daniel Denvir and Alex Lewis.</p>

